### Event 7 - Completion of document processing in the WMS [POST]

<b>Event 7</b> informs about the end of the processing of the entire document in the WMS. Supported event subtypes:
+ 1 - Receipt
+ 2 - Issue note
+ 3 - Order incoming
+ 4 – Production order
+ 5 - Inventory check
+ 6 - Completion of logistics units export
+ 7 - Completion of unloading of the despatch advice 
+ 8 - Completion of pre-receipt returnable packages of the despatch advice
+ 9 - Loading
+ 10 – Receipt – partial completion of document (without completing the receipt)
+ 11 - Completion of inventory transfer request
+ 12 - Completion of logistics' unit export for merged shipments

The processing of an event on the external information system side is conditioned as follows:
+ 1 – Receipt: There is no received event of type 6 or event of type 7 and subtype 10 for the same document that has not been successfully processed on the external information system side.
+ 2 – Issue note: There is no received event of type 5 for the same document that has not been successfully processed on the external information system side.
+ 3 – Order Incoming: There is no received event of type 5 for the same document that has not been successfully processed on the external information system side.
+ 4 – Production order: There is no received event of type 5 for the same document that has not been successfully processed on the external information system side.
+ 5 – Inventory check: The processing of the event on the external information system side is not conditioned by the processing of an event of another type.
+ 6 - Completion of logistics units export: There is no received event of type 26 for the same document that has not been successfully processed on the external information system side.
+ 7 – Completion of unloading of the despatch advice: The processing of the event on the external information system side is not conditioned by the processing of an event of another type.
+ 8 – Completion of pre-receipt returnable packages of the despatch advice: The processing of the event on the external information system side is not conditioned by the processing of an event of another type.
+ 9 – Loading: The processing of the event on the external information system side is not conditioned by the processing of an event of another type.
+ 10 – Receipt – partial completion of receipt (without completing the receipt): The processing of the event on the external information system side is not conditioned by the processing of an event of another type.
+ 11 - Completion of inventory transfer request: The processing of the event on the external information system side is not conditioned by the processing of an event of another type.
+ 12 - Completion of logistics' unit export for merged shipments: There is no received event of type 26 for the same document that has not been successfully processed on the external information system side. It is sent when the last merged shipment is completed.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
        "eventId": "B5E80F04-529F-4F41-8FAC-0DFA2309E6F7",
        "eventType": 7,
        "eventSubtype": 1,
        "documentId": "A4C085B6-C704-4BFF-8384-B9919B282FB8"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
        "data": 
            {
                "id": "erpId_76352839207"
            },
        "errors": []
        }
        
+ Response 400 (application/json)

        {
        "data": null,
        "errors": [
            {
                "errorText": "Unable to process event"
            }
            ]
        }

