### Event 25 - Export of inventory check results  [POST]

<b>Event 25</b> informs about the finished export of inventory check results. It is then possible to use the web service "Inventory check results" to display the exported results.

Element "quantity" shows total number of records exported for the inventory check results.

The processing of an event on the external information system side is conditioned by the processing of an event 7 with subtype 5 for the same document.

+ Request (application/json)

        {
        "eventId": "9AFD7AC9-A791-43DD-BF40-06748BDBC56E",
