            {
                "id": "erpId_76352839225"
            },
        "errors": []
        }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

        {
        "data": null,
        "errors": [
            {
                "errorText": "Unable to process event"
            }
            ]
        }

### Event 26 - Export of logistics units [POST]
<b>Event 26</b> informs about the dispatch of logistics units and their contents. 
Supported event subtypes:
+ 1 - Bulk export of logistics units for the entire document.
+ 2 - Continuous export of each logistics unit.
+ 3 - Bulk export of pre-generated logistics units for the entire document.
+ 4 - Export of parent logistics unit with embedded logistics units.

The processing of an event on the external information system side is conditioned by the processing of an events for the same document in the order in which they were created.

