## About me [/V1/aboutMe/]
Base URI template that is used at the end of the URL when the web service is called: <b>/V1/aboutMe/</b> (example: https://demo.mystock.cz/V1/aboutMe/).

### Get about me [GET /V1/aboutMe/]
About me web service is used to display information about the logged-in user, information about the QAS WMS Interface and also about server throughput.
For each correct call, the result is returned, which is filled with the elements described below. If an error occurs, e.g. a wrongly entered user password, a 403 error is returned and the result set is empty.

Each displayed result has following elements:
+ userName: `U0007_USER` (string) - Logged in user name.
+ localTime: `2023-11-01 13:24:47.093` (datetime) - Time when the service was called.
+ version: `1.247.5690.41` (string) - Version of the QAS WMS Interface.
+ sourceInfo.code: `U0007` (string) - External system code.
+ sourceInfo.type: `mySTOCKInterfaceStandard` (string) - System type.
+ sourceInfo.subType: `Default` (string) - System subtype.
+ environmentInfo.baseServerUrl: `logdemo-wmsint-dev.st.kvados.cz` (string) - URL address of the server.
+ environmentInfo.type: `Development` (string) - Environment type (development, test or production).

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "errors": [],
            "data": {
                "userName": "U0007_USER",
                "localTime": "2023-11-01 13:24:47.093",
                "version": "1.247.5690.41",
                "sourceInfo": {
                    "code": "U0007",
                    "type": "mySTOCKInterfaceStandard",
                    "subType": "Default"
                },
                "environmentInfo": {
                    "baseServerUrl": "logdemo-wmsint-dev.st.kvados.cz",
                    "type": "Development"
                }
            }
        }